description:
Do you ever begin to feel overwhelmed that there are not enough hours in the day? In this course, students will learn to navigate the road of middle school by managing their time effectively. For most students, it may seem impossible to study or finish homework assignments and have time to spend on anything else.

Students can increase their productivity by the following:

  • Implementing practical strategies.
  • Managing their time effectively without falling into traps.
  • Learning how to identify procrastination.
  • Learning how to make decision quickly and effectively.
title: Time Management
